text: Corminboeuf (Dictionnaire-Dikchenéro: Français-Patois/Patê-Franché. Société cantonale des patoisans fribourgeois. Fribourg: 2013. p. 120) is a municipality of the district of Saane in the canton of Fribourg in Switzerland. In 2017 the former municipality of Chésopelloz merged into the municipality of Corminboeuf.Amtliches Gemeindeverzeichnis der Schweiz accessed 10 January 2017 == References == == Other websites == * Official website Category:Municipalities in Sarine
